Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了! 在这边!

Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.11,0:24:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追!


Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个都别放过! 快捉住他们!
;Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个都不要放过! 快捉住他们!

Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下

Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.10,0:24:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?

Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.75,0:24:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢!? 你这家伙!

Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下就饶你们不死

Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则…



Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色头发…

Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脸上的十字刀疤…

Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个「刽子手」

Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.73,0:24:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.38,0:25:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲田老弟  让我来吧

Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤兄!


Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的气味瞒不了我
;Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对血的气味很敏感

Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今有病在身的你  是杀不了他的

Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.59,0:25:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招!
;Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招!


Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:14.18,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)}京都有个被称为刽子手拔刀斋的志士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:14.18,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)}幕府末年——
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:18.38,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手握血刃 开拓出新时代「明治」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:18.38,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他化身修罗 杀人无数
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.39,0:28:21.89,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他却随着动乱终结而销声匿迹——

;Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:14.18,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)}京都有个被称为刽子手拔刀斋的志士
;Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:14.18,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)}幕府末年——
